      <div class="card"><h3>Predictable and cheap</h3><p>One low yearly fee, then a known discounted price at the dentist. For a healthy freelancer who mainly wants cleanings and the occasional filling handled affordably, that predictability is the appeal.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Ready when work is not steady</h3><p>Income can be uneven when you are self-employed. A savings plan keeps dental costs down without a large premium commitment, and it works the moment you need it.</p></div>
